sword swords~
   The spirit seems to turn in your direction, although its head and face are
hidden in darkness.  "The swords.  My swords!  Get them for me!" the spirit
raves.  He mumbles something to himself, then continues.  "Of course.  You
need a reward.  Everyone gets something for their work.  Everyone but poor
Kunji!"
   The spirit quiets down quickly, as if nervous someone or something can
overhear his conversation with you.  "Seven swords were made.  Used to
forge an Empire.  _She_ still controls six of them," he says, hissing the
word "she" as if it were the vilest curse.  "Used me, she did.  But she'll
pay.  At last she'll pay."
   "Get the six.  I'll give you the seventh.  The most powerful.  Trust me."
The figure then shambles off.
~
