torment~
   "Eternal torment!" the spirit cries, when you say the word.  "The
woman is to blame."
   "This is my payment for creating this Empire.  Trapped here by her
magicks."
   The spirit moans, a screeching wail that threatens to burst your
eardrums.  Centuries of pain are behind that cry, an extremely disturbing
sound.
   "I'll have my revenge though.  All I need are the six swords.  Get me
the six and I'll give you the seventh and most powerful."  He wanders off,
mumbling to himself about future plans.
~
