empress~
   "The wench will die, so I swear" the spirit states, his muffled voice
strong with hatred.  "She may believe herself immortal, but I know the
secret.  I know her doom."
   The stories of the founding of the Jade Empire are many.  Most seem to
indicate that the woman known as the Jade Lady or Jade Empress brought
together the noble houses into one powerful Empire.  It was during a time
of chaos and war, with the noble houses fighting one another while goblin
and orc armies ravaged the countryside.  Thousands starved while farms
remained untended, the grain wasted in the fields when the farmers were
run off or slaughtered.
   The Jade Empress, her name lost in time, somehow forged alliances
that formed the backbone of the Empire.  Seven swords were forged by the
master smith Kunji Pishida.  Six were given to nobles of the most powerful
houses while the seventh and most powerful was wielded by the Jade Lady
herself.
~
